{"tid":87105,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全身硬直 印尼女上床要人打橫抬起","createTime":"2017-01-19T14:18:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-10T02:52:52.000Z","uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"76e032b90c5a7ceec9dc3a460d396b870fc40365","tid":87105,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T14:18:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170119&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=56192570\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170119%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D56192570&d=XAwIn4HCiavbvNoE0BIO3n8C1RzHckko4WZAlj2iIrY%3D&h=545b053e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170119%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D56192570&h=c9b70d38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170119&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=56192570</a><br />\n印尼中爪哇一名女子患有嚴重關節疾病，全身硬直，令她不能自理日常生活，就連上床時也要別人把她整個抬起來。<br />\n35歲女子蘇拉米（Sulami）患有強直性脊柱炎（Ankylosing Spondylitis），過去10年無法坐下或彎腰，靠木杖支撐下總算可以步行，起居飲食主要由90歲的祖母照顧。<br />\n強直性脊柱炎是由免疫系統失調所引致，病人脊椎附近的肌腱及韌帶等軟組織發炎鈣化而變得僵硬。假如沒得到有效治療，長期發炎下會令病人脊椎融合，令病人變得全身僵硬，失去活動能力，最終導致殘障或嚴重駝背。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/19/221852_2fe88bff8b5f4ba07f7aec725dde59dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F19%2F221852_2fe88bff8b5f4ba07f7aec725dde59dd.jpg&h=e765ac65&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZGApMwkoj6EULjmENgDzUMLmUoYWgBXWPdMXiWfGv6Ly?filename=u31YwO7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu31YwO7.jpg&h=97087988&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRzJjFdrL6SMaxt8LG51svQZ9aLNPjmw1ckiASCPiqKS9?filename=M9DV3Hj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM9DV3Hj.jpg&h=27da6b0a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/19/221853_c3e77ef235c6605331c458318ba8ead9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F19%2F221853_c3e77ef235c6605331c458318ba8ead9.jpg&h=b06d803f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTmpeQrk4iaKjidp9Hhd7246HxyQHhNMxjSMqgGWH3voJ?filename=6T8P16j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6T8P16j.jpg&h=3e3397ce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee6f67de00f614ab30758f10d9b502d349488775","tid":87105,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T14:19:47.000Z","msg":"好<br />\n我心邪左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52bf95a9b649a19814ff4112400527aa790d749c","tid":87105,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T14:23:20.000Z","msg":"伊斯蘭婦女的理想類型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aedd1efe07c1b87d75f7ecdeaeb146c397273d0","tid":87105,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T23:44:15.000Z","msg":"練咩武功 練到咁樣"},{"pid":"1c3c4e05f1af30b78445f3ed23c91ab2fab6eb90","tid":87105,"uid":47966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T23:52:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好<br />\n我心邪左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31c6f0c8059bdeb81ad35e297189e1275405e57f","tid":87105,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T02:52:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}